    <!-- Project description requirement. Using the abstract from our asignments. -->
    <h1 id="abstract">Abstract:</h1>
    <p>This project builds upon an existing application at the UNR Terawatt Facility. We are adding and improving various functionalities of an automatic gas pressure control system. This system monitors and maintains pressures of sulfur hexafluoride gas in the spark gaps for the Marx generators that supply power to a large pulse generator. The system is responsible for monitoring five circuits. We plan to implement and adapt a larger touchscreen UI, a remote monitoring functionality, robust data integrity checks, and system event logging. This document should serve as a general overview of the project, its impact/significance, and how we plan to manage the development of various subsystems and any associated risks.
    </p>

